body:
@ijuma I think your builder suggestion seems worth investigating.. If we continue with the model of delayed version determination, I was considering whether we could decouple the `Struct` representation from the request objects. Haven't really thought this through, but I was thinking something like this:

```java
public abstract class AbstractRequest {
  abstract Struct toStruct(short version);
}
``` 

That way the request objects remain immutable. I think you also had a suggestion which allowed us to construct the right version up-front.
